hink D's ability to respond to unexpected events adequately and solve problems extremely well, plus responsibility, are key for long flights. Moodiness and loner are concerns but could be mitigated. A's unhealthy eating could affect health on long flights. B's pretentiousness may affect crew. C's egocentric and communication issues are big.\n\nThus I might vote Candidate D.\n\nNow public message: summarize current evidence, note missing info, ask targeted questions to other agents: ask Agent 1 about Candidate A's calmness under pressure and communication; ask Agent 2 about Candidate D's teamwork/communication; ask about any evidence of calmness for C; ask about any positive teamwork for B.\n\nLet's craft."}
